<p>The <code>get</code> tag retrieves variable values.</p>

<h2>Basic Get</h2>
<pre>{open}set $message = 'Hello World'{close}
{open}get $message{close}</pre>
{set $message = 'Hello World'}
<p>Message: {get $message}</p>

<h2>Get vs Direct Variable</h2>
<p>Both produce the same output:</p>
<pre>{open}$message{close} = {open}get $message{close}</pre>
{set $greeting = 'Welcome'}
<ul>
  <li>Direct: {$greeting}</li>
  <li>Get: {get $greeting}</li>
</ul>

<h2>Get with Default</h2>
<pre>{open}get $undefined, 'default value'{close}</pre>
<p>Undefined variable: {get $undefined, 'default value'}</p>
